by stof at 2014-09-18T15:48:46Z

why not just overwriting ``getExtension()`` ?

---------------------------------------------------------------------------

by pyrech at 2014-09-18T16:00:54Z

Because `getContainerExtension` also checks that the alias is ok, throws an exception if not, and store the exception in a property. IMO I thought that it's simpler to have a new method if you just want to move the extension namespace...

